Privacy Policy
Effective Date: 17-06-2025

Cocoon Spa ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application Cocoon Spa.

1. Information We Collect
Personal Information

Name, email address, phone number

Booking details (services selected, time, date)

Payment details (if applicable)

Usage Data

Device information (model, OS)

App interaction logs

IP address and general location (for booking availability)

2. How We Use Your Information
We use the information we collect to:

Provide and manage bookings

Improve user experience

Send appointment confirmations and reminders

Respond to inquiries and support requests

Process payments (if applicable)

3. Sharing Your Information
We do not sell or rent your personal information. We may share your data with:

Spa service providers to fulfill your bookings

Third-party tools (e.g., analytics, payment gateways) under strict confidentiality

Authorities if required by law

4. Data Security
We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your personal data. However, no digital platform can be 100% secure. Use the app at your own risk.

5. Your Rights
You may request to:

Access or update your data

Delete your account and associated data

Withdraw consent for marketing communications

To do so, please contact us at: [your-support@email.com]

6. Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted within the app or on our website.

7. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns, please contact:
Email: support@cocoon.com
